==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: observed
<hw>observed</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>perceived with the
eyes and sometimes with other senses; <as>as, no explanation for the
<ex>observed</ex> phenomena</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Detected by systematic scientific observation;
<as>as, variation in the <ex>observed</ex> flux may depend on a number
of factors</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> ascertained.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Perceived directly with the eyes; observed at first
hand.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> seen, witnessed.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Observer</ent>⟦br⟧
